{"version":1,"built_at":"2026-03-24T20:30:10.168Z","entries":[{"slug":"feedback_melhoria/padrao-evasao-de-pacientes-por-falta-de-vaga-imediata-urgencia-frequenc","path":"C:\\Users\\Brendo\\Documents\\pediatria-v2\\clinica-vault\\memories\\feedback_melhoria\\padrao-evasao-de-pacientes-por-falta-de-vaga-imediata-urgencia-frequenc.md","content":"**Padrão:** Desistência por percepção de custo-benefício e serviços agregados\n**Frequência:** Média — 4 casos recentes de evasão por preço.\n**Observação:** Pacientes desistem não apenas pelo valor absoluto, mas quando percebem que estão pagando por serviços que não precisam (ex: consulta casada com nutricionista) ou quando não há flexibilidade/descontos para exames específicos (ex: teste do pezinho).\n**Impacto financeiro/operacional:** Perda direta de receita (aprox. R$ 2.000 em 4 dias) por rigidez na formatação dos pacotes de consulta e exames.\n**Ação recomendada:** Avaliar a possibilidade de desmembrar serviços (ex: consulta pediátrica sem nutricionista inclusa) e criar margem de negociação para exames avulsos.","memory_type":"padrao_comportamental","quality_score":100,"connections":[],"updated_at":"2026-03-24T20:30:10.166Z"}],"embeddings":{"feedback_melhoria/padrao-evasao-de-pacientes-por-falta-de-vaga-imediata-urgencia-frequenc":[-0.0071962574,-0.01877945,-0.004095137,-0.048576236,0.008404225,-0.009153689,-0.0024030595,0.008766716,-0.019001486,-0.0052252337,0.016437897,0.015002838,0.004242153,-0.014257182,0.10533182,0.012773776,0.022645134,0.022207923,0.0015382008,0.0033108168,0.018375052,0.032828286,-0.031757828,-0.016028535,0.00006687613,-0.01856137,0.03285752,-0.014802768,0.042743936,0.028268613,0.02096458,0.016515143,0.021133216,0.026661633,0.0041528633,0.011928883,0.009095366,0.009138369,-0.009961773,0.028383074,0.011889306,0.0018773566,0.009962401,0.0172126,-0.0028570278,0.0039571435,0.0026782516,-0.021235099,0.0008520674,0.018123988,-0.0034929244,-0.0008660004,0.00023855567,-0.16330908,-0.029227292,-0.013699296,0